OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering showers in the north dying
OL,7,Fout, leaving a dry night with clear
OL,8,Fspells, and overnight temperatures a
OL,9,Flittle cooler than of late especially
OL,10,Fin rural spots. The odd mist or fog
OL,11,Fpatch developing in prone areas. Wind
OL,12,Feasing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,15,Fwarm or very warm for many again on
OL,16,FSaturday. However, cloud thickening
OL,17,Flater, with some outbreaks of
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy rain during the
OL,19,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
